replies.msg:
Jordi Alba: &quot;The sensations are almost the same as in 2015 with the treble. We're in the Copa final, we're still in the Champions League and we're going well in La Liga. But we're talking of two different coaches, two who work really well but it's difficult to compare.&quot;<br />
<br />
&quot;You have to think quickly to play with Leo. Messi is a different player, one who makes you better. The quality and work he's been producing in La Liga is ridiculous. It's an honor to play alongside him.&quot;

